Güçlü Hasta İlişkileri</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Ziyaretler arasında güven ve bakımın sürekliliğini inşa eder.</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-teal-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4">Sağlayıcı Kontrolü</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Yanıt pencerelerini siz belirlersiniz, iletişimin yönetilebilir kalmasını sağlarsınız.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-light/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30">Asenkron Tele-sağlık Mesajlaşması</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Asenkron Tele-sağlık Mesajlaşması</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Hastaların bağlamla birlikte sorular gönderdiği ve sağlayıcıların belirlenmiş yanıt pencereleri içinde yanıt verdiği güvenli bir hasta mesajlaşma sistemi - yapılandırılmış bakım, gerçek zamanlı sohbet değil.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Hasta Soru Gönderimi</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Hastalar portal veya uygulama üzerinden sağlık soruları gönderir, rapor veya görüntü ekleme seçeneğiyle.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Sağlayıcı Yanıt Sistemi</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sağlayıcılar, bakımı verimli ve yönetilebilir tutarak tanımlanan zaman dilimleri içinde kendi programlarına göre yanıt verir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Entegre İş Akışı</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Tüm sorular ve cevaplar, bakımın sürekliliğini destekleyerek hastanın sağlık kaydında saklanır.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Soru Yönetimi Gösterge Paneli</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sağlayıcılar ve ekipler, hasta sorularını tek bir düzenli görünümde takip eder, önceliklendirir ve yönetir.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Async telehealth messaging interface" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fasynchronous-telehealth-messaging.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Integrated payment processing for patient messaging" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-payments-for-patient-messaging.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Entegre Ödemeler</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Hasta Mesajlaşması İçin Entegre Ödemeler</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Sağlayıcı zamanını tazmin edilen bakıma dönüştürün - her mesajlaşma karşılaşması, Virtual Practice&#x27;ınız aracılığıyla faturalandırılabilir, takip edilebilir ve ödenebilir.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-dollar-sign h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Sağlayıcı Başına Fiyatlandırma</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Her sağlayıcı için rollerine veya uzmanlıklarına göre farklı hizmet ücretleri belirleyin.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Otomatik Faturalandırma ve Ödemeler</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Mesajlaşma karşılaşmaları için faturalar otomatik olarak oluşturulur. Hastalar çevrimiçi güvenli bir şekilde ödeme yapar ve fonlar doğrudan kliniğinizin hesabına gider.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Yapılandırılabilir Takip Notları</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Belirlenmiş sayıda takip yanıtının bir karşılaşma ücreti içine dahil edilmesine izin verin. Gerektiğinde ek notlar ayrıca faturalandırılabilir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Sağlayıcı Zamanı İçin Adil Değer</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Artık ücretsiz aramalar, SMS veya WhatsApp mesajları yok. Sağlayıcı zamanı, yapılandırılmış, faturalandırılabilir mesajlaşma yoluyla uygun şekilde tazmin edilir.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-purple-light/20 text-purple-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-purple-accent/30">Entegre Uygulama İş Akışı</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Entegre Uygulama İş Akışı</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Hasta Mesajlaşması izole bir araç değildir - Virtual Practice&#x27;ınızın bir parçasıdır ve her mesajın güvenli, bağlamsal ve eyleme dönüştürülebilir olmasını sağlar.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Bağlam Açısından Zengin Yanıtlar</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sağlayıcılar, sağlık izleyici verileri ve önceki konsültasyonlar dahil olmak üzere hastanın sağlık kaydından tam bağlamla yanıt verir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Kalıcı Kayıt</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sorular ve yanıtlar, gelecekteki referans ve bakımın sürekliliği için hastanın kaydında saklanır.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Eyleme Dönüştürülebilir İş Akışları</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Herhangi bir mesajdan sağlayıcılar randevu planlayabilir, konsültasyon belgesi ekleyebilir, reçete yazabilir veya hastayı bir bakım planına atayabilir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Yeni Hastaları İşe Alma</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">İkinci görüş arayanlar veya ilk kez temas edenler, portal aracılığıyla kayıtlı hasta olarak sorunsuz bir şekilde kaydedilir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Otomatik Bildirimler</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Yeni sorular geldiğinde sağlayıcılara uyarı verilir; yanıtlar hazır olduğunda hastalara bildirilir - e-posta, SMS veya uygulama bildirimi yoluyla.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Entegre Faturalandırma</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Her karşılaşma otomatik olarak bir fatura oluşturabilir; ödemeler çevrimiçi toplanır ve doğrudan kliniğin hesabına aktarılır.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Integrated practice workflow dashboard" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fintegrated-practice-workflow.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Secure and compliant communication platform" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_messaging%2Fsecure-and-compliant-communication.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-teal-primary/20 text-teal-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-teal-primary/30">Güvenli ve Uyumlu İletişim</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Güvenli ve Uyumlu İletişim</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Hasta mesajlaşması güvenli, özel ve uyumlu olmalıdır. HIPAA veya GDPR uyumlu olmayan e-posta, SMS veya tüketici uygulamalarının aksine, bu özellik her değişimin korunmasını ve Virtual Practice&#x27;ınız içinde sorumlu bir şekilde saklanmasını sağlar.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Uçtan Uca Şifreleme</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Tüm hasta mesajları, ekleri ve sağlayıcı yanıtları aktarım sırasında ve dinlenme halinde şifrelenir.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">HIPAA ve GDPR Uyumluluğu</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sağlık için inşa edilmiştir - iletişimler en katı güvenlik ve gizlilik standartlarını karşılar.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Sağlık Kayıtlarıyla Entegre</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Konuşmalar, güvensiz uygulamalara dağılmak yerine otomatik olarak hastanın elektronik sağlık kaydına bağlanır.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Sağlayıcılar ve Hastalar İçin Gönül Rahatlığı</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">İletişimin güvenli, denetlenebilir ve uyumlu olduğunu bilerek güvenle soruları yanıtlayın.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-vibrant/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30 mb-6">KULLANIM SENARYOLARI</span></div><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-8 mt-4">Yaygın Hasta Mesajlaşma Senaryoları</h2></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-green-success/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-8 w-8 text-green-success" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Takipler</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">İlaç soruları, iyileşme kontrolleri, sonuç açıklamaları</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-blue-vibrant/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-8 w-8 text-blue-vibrant" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Kronik Bakım</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Diyabet, hipertansiyon, astım için sürekli rehberlik</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-purple-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-8 w-8 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">İkinci Görüşler</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Raporları güvenli bir şekilde inceleyin ve yeni hastalara profesyonel rehberlik sağlayın</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-teal-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">İlk Temas</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Tam konsültasyonlara yol açan güvenli, belgelenmiş ilişkiler başlatın</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Allowing doctors to offer telemedicine, remote monitoring health plans, collect payments and the health blog are some of the best features of the Virtual Practice®.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Gerard Saltibus MD</p><p class="text-gray-600">General Practitioner, St. Lucia</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is patient messaging in telehealth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patient Messaging is a secure, HIPAA/GDPR-compliant way for patients to send health questions to their provider between visits. Unlike live chat, it's asynchronous — providers respond within defined timeframes, not in real time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why should my clinic use secure patient messaging instead of SMS or WhatsApp?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SMS and consumer apps aren't secure, compliant, or integrated into your workflow. Secure patient messaging keeps communication encrypted, linked to each patient's health record, and billable — so providers are fairly compensated for their time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers bill for patient messages?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging can be configured as a billable service with provider-specific pricing. Bills are auto-generated, patients pay online, and funds are transferred directly to your clinic's account. You can also configure follow-up notes within each encounter."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging integrate with the health record?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every question and response is stored in the patient's health record, alongside their health tracker data, labs, and consultations. Providers can schedule appointments, create documents, or assign care plans based on the perspective from a message thread."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is this feature useful for second opinions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging is ideal for patients seeking second opinions or initial guidance. New patients submitting questions through your portal are seamlessly onboarded as registered patients in your Virtual Practice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do notifications work for patient messaging?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Automated notifications are sent at key points: providers receive alerts when a new question arrives, and patients are notified when a response is ready. Notifications can be delivered by email, SMS, or app push."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients attach reports or images to their questions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can include lab results, medical reports, or photos with their messages, giving providers richer context when responding."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging help prevent patients from relying only on AI tools?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When patients don't have easy access to their providers, they often turn to search engines or AI tools for answers. Patient Messaging ensures they can reach their own doctor directly — securely, professionally, and with full context from their health record."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is patient messaging only for established patients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. It's valuable both for existing patients (follow-ups, chronic care, medication questions) and for new patients (initial contact, second opinions). It helps providers grow their patient base while improving continuity of care."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does patient messaging save time for providers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Because it's asynchronous, providers can respond on their schedule within set response windows. This avoids interruptions from phone calls or SMS, reduces no-shows, and ensures that time spent answering patient questions is properly compensated."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What is patient messaging in telehealth?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What is patient messaging in telehealth?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Why should my clinic use secure patient messaging instead of SMS or WhatsApp?" class="w-full tex